Glasses.

15
00:00:39,438 --> 00:00:41,940
Like my dad is-- 
my dad goes to work in Oakland

16
00:00:41,974 --> 00:00:43,475
and he has a computer

17
00:00:43,509 --> 00:00:45,210
and he just works 
every day on his computer.

18
00:00:45,244 --> 00:00:47,379
(interviewer) 
Is that pretty cool? 
Or is that not so cool?

19
00:00:47,412 --> 00:00:50,415
It's cool 'cause I get to 
go down a slide in his office.

20
00:00:50,449 --> 00:00:53,519
(interviewer) 
Do you think it'd be fun to be 
a computer science person?

21
00:00:53,552 --> 00:00:57,322
- I don't think so. 
