22
00:00:57,356 --> 00:00:58,924
Because you're always 
on a computer

23
00:00:58,957 --> 00:01:00,492
and it sometimes 
could get a little boring.

24
00:01:00,526 --> 00:01:03,462
(interviewer) 
And that image in your mind, 
is that a man or a woman?

25
00:01:03,495 --> 00:01:04,796
Man.

