00:01:25,984 --> 00:01:27,653
(Reshma Saujani) 
The White House 
released a report

30
00:01:27,686 --> 00:01:29,488
that there will be 
1.4 million jobs

31
00:01:29,521 --> 00:01:30,956
that are gonna be open 
by 2020

32
00:01:30,989 --> 00:01:32,824
in the computing-related 
fields.

33
00:01:32,858 --> 00:01:35,561
