In the next 5 years, 
this country is going to produce

37
00:01:43,402 --> 00:01:45,871
about 3 times as many jobs 
for software engineers

38
00:01:45,904 --> 00:01:48,974
as it is producing 
new computer science majors.

39
00:01:49,908 --> 00:01:54,546
♪♪♪

40
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:57,015
This whole industry is gonna 
start to run out of gas

41
00:01:57,049 --> 00:01:59,918
if we're not producing 
enough computer science talent.

42
00:01:59,952 --> 00:02:01,853
It's so urgent 
that we get more people

43
00:02:01,887 --> 00:02:04,389
to have the skills 
for coding and making,

44
00:02:04,423 --> 00:02:06,725
'cause we have so many different 
problems to solve in the world.

45
00:02:06,758 --> 00:02:09,394
And the industry 
really needs more diversity

46
00:02:09,428 --> 00:02:11,063
so we can make 
the broad set of products

47
00:02:11,096 --> 00:02:12,998
that this world deserves.

48
00:02:13,031 --> 00:02:15,701
And I really think that this 
is a Rosie the Riveter moment,

49
00:02:15,734 --> 00:02:17,803
because the jobs are here

50
00:02:17,836 --> 00:02:20,005
and we don't have 
the workers to fill them.

51
